<LogsScreen@MDScreen>:
    name: "Log"

    MDBoxLayout:
        orientation: "vertical"

        MDToolbar:
            title: f"[font=Icons]{md_icons['folder']}[/font] Logs"
            left_action_items: [["menu", lambda x: app.root.get_screen("maininfo").ids.nav_drawer.set_state("open")]]
            right_action_items: [["close", lambda x: app.root.get_screen("maininfo").close()]]

        ScrollView:
            bar_width: "8dp"
            bar_color: C('FFFFFF')

            MDBoxLayout:
                orientation: "vertical"
                size_hint: None, None
                height: self.minimum_height
                size: (root.width, root.height)
                spacing: "8dp"
                padding: "8dp"

                MDLabel:
                    adaptive_height: True
                    text_color: C('FFFFFF')
                    theme_text_color: "Custom"
                    font_style: 'H6'
                    text: "Introduction"
                    markup: True

                MDLabel:
                    adaptive_height: True
                    text_color: app.theme_cls.primary_color
                    theme_text_color: "Custom"
                    font_style: 'Body2'
                    text: "In the beginning of each round, one or more logs are provided to the entire group. Depending on the round, will depend on how many and what type of log is provided. Logs will never provide definite information. Players consistently found on logs do not necessarily prove guilt. However, a hacker will always be on every log."

                MDSeparator:
                    color: C("FFFFFF")

                MDLabel:
                    adaptive_height: True
                    text_color: C('FFFFFF')
                    theme_text_color: "Custom"
                    font_style: 'H6'
                    text: "Legend"
                    markup: True

                MDLabel:
                    text_color: app.theme_cls.primary_color
                    font_style: "Body2"
                    text: f"[size=22sp][font=Icons]{md_icons['folder']}[/font][/size][color=#FFFFFF]: Unrevealed Evidence[/color]"
                    theme_text_color: "Custom"
                    adaptive_height: True
                    markup: True

                MDLabel:
                    text_color: C('FFFFFF')
                    font_style: "Body2"
                    text: f"[color=#1565c0][size=22sp][font=Icons]{md_icons['folder-key']}[/font][/size][/color]: Exclusive Evidence"
                    theme_text_color: "Custom"
                    adaptive_height: True
                    markup: True

                MDLabel:
                    text_color: C('FFFFFF')
                    font_style: "Body2"
                    text: f"[size=22sp][font=Icons]{md_icons['folder-account']}[/font][/size]: Revealed Evidence"
                    theme_text_color: "Custom"
                    adaptive_height: True
                    markup: True

                MDLabel:
                    text_color: C('FFFFFF')
                    font_style: "Body2"
                    text: f"[size=22sp][color=#c62828][font=Icons]{md_icons['folder-alert']}[/font][/color][/size]: Corrupted Evidence"
                    theme_text_color: "Custom"
                    adaptive_height: True
                    markup: True

                MDSeparator:
                    color: C("FFFFFF")

                MDLabel:
                    adaptive_height: True
                    text_color: C('FFFFFF')
                    theme_text_color: "Custom"
                    font_style: 'H6'
                    text: "Evidence"

                MDLabel:
                    adaptive_height: True
                    text_color: app.theme_cls.primary_color
                    theme_text_color: "Custom"
                    font_style: 'Body2'
                    text: f"Each [size=22sp][color=#FFFFFF][font=Icons]{md_icons['folder']}[/font][/color][/size] is evidence of a player that is on the log. Once a log is uploaded by pressing the [color=#FFFFFF][size=22sp][font=Icons]{md_icons['cloud-upload']}[/font][/size][/color], the evidence will become [color=#FFFFFF][size=22sp][font=Icons]{md_icons['folder-account']}[/font][/size][/color] and the color of the evidence will signify who it belongs to. There is a probability where logs may be exactly the same. This is an intended and should be taken into consideration."
                    markup: True

                MDSeparator:
                    color: C("FFFFFF")

                MDLabel:
                    adaptive_height: True
                    text_color: C('FFFFFF')
                    theme_text_color: "Custom"
                    font_style: 'H6'
                    text: "Corrupted Log"

                MDLabel:
                    adaptive_height: True
                    text_color: app.theme_cls.primary_color
                    theme_text_color: "Custom"
                    font_style: 'Body2'
                    text: f"There is a seventy percent chance of a log failing when it is being revealed. This percentage may have been tampered with by other players. When a log becomes corrupted, all unrevealed evidence becomes [size=22sp][color=#FFFFFF][font=Icons]{md_icons['folder-alert']}[/font][/color][/size] and no further information is provided. Only player logs cannot be corrupted. Corrupted logs may be recovered by actions."
                    markup: True

                MDSeparator:
                    color: C("FFFFFF")

                MDLabel:
                    adaptive_height: True
                    text_color: C('FFFFFF')
                    theme_text_color: "Custom"
                    font_style: 'H6'
                    text: "Player Log"

                MDLabel:
                    adaptive_height: True
                    text_color: app.theme_cls.primary_color
                    theme_text_color: "Custom"
                    font_style: 'Body2'
                    text: f"Player logs are found on the 3rd round and are identified by two [color=#FFFFFF][size=22sp][font=Icons]{md_icons['folder-key']}[/font][/size][/color]. A player log can be opened by the pressing the [color=#FFFFFF][size=22sp][font=Icons]{md_icons['cloud']}[/font][/size][/color]. Once opened, it will reveal who the log belongs to. Only the owner of the log can upload and view its revealed contents. The player who owns the log will never be within their own log. One player cannot have multiple player logs nor can an AI get a player log."
                    markup: True